1,"keywords":[{"id":159551,"name":"pink film"},{"id":328767,"name":"gay pink film"}]}},"person_4169_translations":{"at":1772689441731,"data":{"id":4169,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"David Khari Webber \"Dave\" Chappelle was born on August 24, 1973 in Washington, D.C. He is a comedian, screenwriter, television/film producer and actor. Chappelle began his film career in the film Robin Hood: Men in Tights in 1993 and continued to star in minor roles in the films The Nutty Professor, Con Air, and Blue Streak. His first lead role in a film was in Half Baked in 1998. In 2003, he became widely known for his popular sketch comedy television series, Chappelle's Show, which ran until 2006. Comedy Central ranked him forty-third in its list of the 100 greatest stand-up comedians","name":"Dave Chappelle","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"GR","iso_639_1":"el","name":"ελληνικά","english_name":"Greek","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"David Khari Webber „Dave“ Chappelle wurde am 24. August 1973 in Washington, D.C. geboren.\n\nEr ist Komiker, Drehbuchautor, Fernseh-/Filmproduzent und Schauspieler. Chappelle begann seine Filmkarriere 1993 mit dem Film Robin Hood – Helden in Strumpfhosen und spielte danach kleinere Rollen in den Filmen Der verrückte Professor, Con Air und Blue Streak. Seine erste Hauptrolle in einem Film hatte er 1998 in Half Baked. 2003 wurde er weithin bekannt durch seine beliebte Sketch-Comedy-Fernsehserie Chappelle’s Show, die bis 2006 lief. Comedy Central platzierte ihn auf Platz 43 seiner Liste der 100 größten Stand-up-Comedians.\n\nGoogle Übersetzung","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"FR","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français","english_name":"French","data":{"biography":"David Chappelle, dit Dave Chappelle, né le 24 août 1973 à Washington, D.C., est un humoriste, acteur, scénariste et producteur américain.\n\nChappelle est un artiste populaire de la télévision américaine, notamment avec son émission de sketches Chappelle's Show, diffusée sur Comedy Central de 2003 à 2006.\n\nHéritier d'un humour noir proche de Richard Pryor (acteur culte des Nuits de Harlem), il est connu pour son ton de scène engagé, décapant et parfois agressif.","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"데이브 샤펠","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"BR","iso_639_1":"pt","name":"Português","english_name":"Portuguese","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"David Khari Webber “Dave” Chappelle 于 1973 年 8 月 24 日出生于华盛顿特区。他是喜剧演员、编剧、电视/电影制片人和演员。Chappelle 于 1993 年在电影《罗宾汉：紧身衣的男人》中开始了他的电影生涯，并继续在电影《疯狂教授》、《Con Air》和《Blue Streak》中出演次要角色。他第一次在电影中担任主角是在 1998 年的《半生不熟》中。2003 年，他因广受欢迎的小品喜剧电视连续剧《查佩尔的秀》而广为人知，该剧一直持续到 2006 年。喜剧中心将他排在 100 位最伟大的单口喜剧演员名单中的第 43 位","name":"大卫·查普尔","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RS","iso_639_1":"sr","name":"Srpski","english_name":"Serbian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Дејв Шапел","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"UA","iso_639_1":"uk","name":"Український","english_name":"Ukrainian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Дейв Шапел","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Дэйв Шапелл","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IN","iso_639_1":"ml","name":"","english_name":"Malayalam","data":{"biography":"","name":"ഡേവ് ഷപ്പെൽ","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IR","iso_639_1":"fa","name":"فارسی","english_name":"Persian","data":{"biography":"","name":"دیو چاپله","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IN","iso_639_1":"hi","name":"हिन्दी","english_name":"Hindi","data":{"biography":"","name":"डेव चैपल","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IL","iso_639_1":"he","name":"עִבְרִית","english_name":"Hebrew","data":{"biography":"","name":"דייב שאפל","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"BD","iso_639_1":"bn","name":"বাংলা","english_name":"Bengali","data":{"biography":"","name":"ডেভ চ্যাপেল","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"BG","iso_639_1":"bg","name":"български език","english_name":"Bulgarian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Дейв Шапел","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HY","iso_639_1":"hy","name":"","english_name":"Armenian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Դեյվ Շափել","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"SA","iso_639_1":"ar","name":"العربية","english_name":"Arabic","data":{"biography":"","name":"ديف شبيل","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"デイヴ・シャペル","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"David Khari Webber “Dave” Chappelle 於 1973 年 8 月 24 日出生於華盛頓特區。他是喜劇演員、編劇、電視/電影製片人和演員。Chappelle 於 1993 年在電影《羅賓漢：緊身衣的男人》中開始了他的電影生涯，並繼續在電影《瘋狂教授》、《Con Air》和《Blue Streak》中出演次要角色。他第一次在電影中擔任主角是在 1998 年的《半生不熟》中。2003 年，他因廣受歡迎的小品喜劇電視聯續劇《查佩爾的秀》而廣為人知，該劇一直持續到 2006 年。喜劇中心將他排在 100 位最偉大的單口喜劇演員名單中的第 43 位","name":"大衞·查普爾","primary":false}}]}},"person_1136405_translations":{"at":1772689449669,"data":{"id":1136405,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Terence Tsui","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"小肥，原名徐智勇，澳门歌手、演员，1976年生。2003年参加第一届澳广视至爱新听力颁奖音乐会，并获得金奖。 澳门发展期间，小肥在酒廊献唱并自资出碟，又与钟楚霖组成组合C-Plus。2007年以艺名“小肥”到香港发展。  除音乐外，小肥亦参与电影拍摄工作，2008年参演《爱斗大》。2009年参演电影《关人7事》。2011年出演钟澍佳执导的电影《夏日恋神马》。2014年1月在澳门威尼斯人金光综艺馆举行首个个人大型演唱会。","name":"小肥","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"小肥，原名小肥，澳門歌手、演員，1976 年生。2003 年參加第一屆澳廣視至愛新聽力頒獎音樂會，並獲得金獎。\n\n澳門發展期間，小肥在酒廊獻唱並自資出碟，又與鍾楚霖組成組合 C - Plus。2007 年以藝名“小肥”到香港發展。\n\n除音樂外，小肥亦參與電影拍攝工作，2008 年參演《愛鬥大》。2009 年參演電影《關人 7 事》。2011 年出演鍾澍佳執導的電影《戀夏戀夏戀戀下》。2014 年 1 月在澳門威尼斯人金光綜藝館舉行首個個人大型演唱會。","name":"小肥","primary":true}}]}},"person_22125_translations":{"at":1772689451435,"data":{"id":22125,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Jimmi Simpson (born November 21, 1975) is an American stage, film and television actor, best known for his recurring roles in television series, such as House of Cards, It's Always Sunny in Philadelphia, Psych, and Westworld.","name":"Jimmi Simpson","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"PL","iso_639_1":"pl","name":"Polski","english_name":"Polish","data":{"biography":"James Raymond (Jimmi) Simpson (ur. 21 listopada 1975 w Hackettstown) – amerykański aktor teatralny, filmowy i telewizyjny. Były mąż aktorki Melanie Lynskey.\n\nStudiował aktorstwo na Bloomsburg University of Pennsylvania, następnie grywał w grupie teatralnej Williamstown Theatre Festival z Massachusetts. W latach 2007–2008 występował na Broadwayu w jednej z głównych ról sztuki The Farnsworth Invention nagrodzonej Theatre World Award. Jako aktor filmowy debiutował w 2000 we Frajerze u boku m.in. Jasona Biggsa. Otrzymywał później gościnne role w kolejnych filmach (m.in. Garbi: super bryka, Zodiak, Abraham Lincoln: Łowca wampirów, Świat w płomieniach). Występował cyklicznie w talk-show Late Show with David Letterman. Dołączał do regularnych ekip seriali U nas w Filadelfii, Breakout Kings, House of Cards, Newsroom czy Westworld.","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"지미 심슨","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"吉米·辛普森出生在新泽西州的哈克特斯敦，于宾州布鲁姆斯堡大学毕业，并获得戏剧学士学位，在马萨诸塞州的威廉斯敦剧院演出了4年。2000年，吉米·辛普森在青少年喜剧片《窝囊废》中首次亮相。2008年，吉米·辛普森在百老汇主演《费罗·法恩斯沃斯的发明》 ，他的表现赢得了“