:"Azwaa Amalya Diandra","original_name":"Azwaa Amalya Diandra","popularity":0.4553,"profile_path":null,"credit_id":"68921221312d38eebeb7f9c8","department":"Production","job":"Production Assistant"}]}},"person_1649152_translations":{"at":1772689458644,"data":{"id":1649152,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Jacob Batalon (/ˌbɑːtəˈlɒn, ˈbætəˌlɒn/) is an American actor. He had his breakout role as Ned Leeds in the Marvel Cinematic Universe beginning with Spider-Man: Homecoming (2017) and its sequels, Far From Home (2019) and No Way Home (2021), along with cameo appearances in Avengers: Infinity War (2018) and Avengers: Endgame (2019).\n\nDescription above from the Wikipedia article Jacob Batalon, licensed under CC-BY-SA, full list of contributors on Wikipedia.","name":"Jacob Batalon","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"ES","iso_639_1":"es","name":"Español","english_name":"Spanish","data":{"biography":"Jacob Batalon (9 de octubre de 1996)​ es un actor estadounidense. Hizo su debut como actor en 2016 en la película North Woods como Cooper; en 2017 forma parte del elenco principal de la película Spider-Man: Homecoming, en el papel de Ned Leeds.\n\nEs conocido por interpretar a Ned Leeds en las películas del Universo cinematográfico de Marvel Spider-Man: Homecoming (2017), Avengers: Infinity War (2018), Avengers: Endgame (2019) y Spider-Man: Far From Home (2019).","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"제이콥 배털런","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TR","iso_639_1":"tr","name":"Türkçe","english_name":"Turkish","data":{"biography":"Jacob Batalon ( / ˌ b ɑː t ə l ɒ n , b ± t ə ˌ l ɒ n /, 9 Ekim 1996  doğumlu) Amerikalı aktör,  en çok Marvel Sinematik Evreninde (MCU) Örümcek Adam (Spider Man)  filmlerindeki Ned Leeds rolüyle biliniyor.  Şu ana kadar Eve Dönüş: Örümcek Adam (2017), Örümcek Adam: Evden Uzak (2019), Örümcek Adam: No Way Home (2021), Avengers: Sonsuz Savaş (2018) ve The Avengers: oyun sonu(2019) filmlerinde Ned Leeds olarak rol aldı.\n\nBatalon, Hawaii, Honolulu'da Filipinli bir ailenin çocuğu olarak dünyaya geldi. Özel Katolik okulu St. Anthony's School'dan mezun olduktan sonra, Damien Memorial School'a gitti , ardından Batalon , müzik teorisi okumak için Kapi'olani Community College'a gitti , ancak daha sonra okulu bıraktı. Daha sonra New York Konservatuarı Dramatik Sanatlar'da oyunculuk eğitimi almak için iki yıllık bir program aldı.  Batalon ilk oyunculuk deneyimini 2016 yapımı North Woods filminde yaptı.  2017'de Batalon, Spider-Man: Homecoming'de Peter Parker'ın en iyi arkadaşı Ned olarak ilk büyük rolünü aldı . Yenilmezler: Sonsuzluk Savaşı , Yenilmezler: Oyun Sonu ve Örümcek Adam: Evden Uzakta'daki rolünü tekrarladı.  2020'de Batalon, Spider-Man: No Way Home'daki rolü için 102 pound (46 kg) kilo verdi.","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"FR","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français","english_name":"French","data":{"biography":"Jacob Batalon (né le 9 octobre 1996, à Honolulu, Hawaï) est un acteur américain d'origine philippine, connu pour son rôle de Ned Leeds dans les films du Marvel Cinematic Universe (MCU), Spider-Man: Homecoming (2017), Avengers: Infinity War (2018), Avengers: Endgame (2019), Spider-Man: Far From Home (2019) et Spider-Man: No Way Home (2021).","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"SA","iso_639_1":"ar","name":"العربية","english_name":"Arabic","data":{"biography":"ممثل أمريكي، ولد في 9 أكتوبر 1996، في هونولولو، هاواي، الولايات المتحدة الأمريكية، اشتهر بعمله في فيلم (Spider-Man: Homecoming) عام 2017، وفيلم (Every Day) عام 2018، وفيلم (Avengers: Infinity War) عام 2018، وغيرها من الأعمال.","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"雅各布·貝塔隆","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"💥Джейкоб Андрес Баталон. Родился в 1996-ом году в Гонолулу, Гавайи, США. Был единственным ребёнком в семье. Отец работал рабочим, а мать была медсестрой. Учился в Капиоланийском общественном колледже. Работает актёром. С 2025-го женат на дизайнере Веронике Лихов, детей у пары нет\n\n🏆Главные награды🏆: Teen Choice Awards (2017) [Человек-паук: Возвращение домой]\n\n🎬Главные проекты🎬: «Человек-паук: Возвращение домой» (2017), «Мстители: Война бесконечности» (2018), «Мстители: Финал» (2019)\n\n⭐Интересный факт⭐: Джейкоб сбросил около 45-50 кг ради лучшей физической формы и работы над собой, направленной не только на внешность, но и на здоровье","name":"Джейкоб Баталон","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"雅各布·贝塔隆是一位美国演员。从《蜘蛛侠：英雄归来》（2017 年）及其续集《英雄远征》（2019 年）和《无路可归》（2021 年）开始，他在漫威电影宇宙中饰演内德·利兹 （Ned Leeds） 的突破性角色，并在《复仇者联盟：无限战争》（2018 年）和《复仇者联盟：终局之战》（2019 年）中客串。","name":"雅各布·贝塔隆","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"BR","iso_639_1":"pt","name":"Português","english_name":"Portuguese","data":{"biography":"Jacob Batalon é um ator americano que teve seu papel de destaque como Ned Leeds no Universo Cinematográfico Marvel, começando com Homem-Aranha: De Volta ao Lar (2017) e suas sequências, Longe de Casa (2019) e De jeito nenhum para casa (2021), junto com aparições em Vingadores: Guerra Infinita. (2018) e Vingadores: Ultimato (2019).","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"積及·巴特朗是一位美國演員。從《蜘蛛俠：英雄歸來》（2017 年）及其續集《英雄遠征》（2019 年）和《無路可歸》（2021 年）開始，他在漫威電影宇宙中飾演內德·利茲 （Ned Leeds） 的突破性角色，並在《復仇者聯盟：無限戰爭》（2018 年）和《復仇者聯盟 4：終局之戰》（2019 年）中客串。","name":"積及·巴特朗","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"ジェイコブ・バタロン","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"PL","iso_639_1":"pl","name":"Polski","english_name":"Polish","data":{"biography":"Jacob Batalon (/ˌbɑːtəˈlɒn, ˈbætəˌlɒn/) jest amerykańskim aktorem. Przełomową rolę zagrał Ned Leeds w Marvel Cinematic Universe, zaczynając od Spider-Man: Homecoming (2017) i jego sequeli, Daleko od domu (2019) i Bez drogi do domu (2021), a także pojawił się w epizodycznych rolach w Avengers: Wojna bez granic (2018) i Avengers: Koniec gry (2019).\n\nOpis powyżej pochodzi z artykułu Wikipedii Jacob Batalon, licencjonowanego na podstawie CC-BY-SA, pełna lista współpracowników na Wikipedii.","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"UA","iso_639_1":"uk","name":"Український","english_name":"Ukrainian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Джейкоб Баталон","primary":false}}]}},"person_3684753_translations":{"at":1772689458867,"data":{"id":3684753,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Andre Yllana is a Filipino actor.","name":"Andre Yllana","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"PH","iso_639_1":"tl","name":"","english_name":"Tagalog","data":{"biography":"","name":"Andre Yllana","primary":true}}]}},"person_556488_translations":{"at":1772689459509,"data":{"id":556488,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Nathalie Söderqvist","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"SE","iso_639_1":"sv","name":"svenska","english_name":"Swedish","data":{"biography":"","name":"Nathalie Söderqvist","primary":true}}]}},"person_1963342_translations":{"at":1772689480934,"data":{"id":1963342,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Shivankit Singh Parihar","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IN","iso_639_1":"hi","name":"हिन्दी","english_name":"Hindi","data":{"biography":"","name":"Shivankit Singh Parihar","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}}]}}}}